75  /// instructions, this will return the register class that has been defined

87  /// a MOV. For example:
88  /// ADD_I32_e32 VGPR0, 15
89  /// to
90  /// MOV VGPR1, 15
91  /// ADD_I32_e32 VGPR0, VGPR1
